videos.headline: Brown breaks off 56-yard run
videos.description: Jordon Brown takes the hand off for a big gain early in the 1st quarter.

videos.headline: Quarterman's sack ends UNC's drive
videos.description: Shaquille Quarterman brings down Chazz Surratt on 4th and goal.

videos.headline: Homer picks up 35 using ref as a pick
videos.description: Travis Homer loses defender when he runs into the referee, allowing him to pick up 35 yards.

videos.headline: Elliott makes 33-yard reception on trick play
videos.description: UNC's backup quarterback comes up with 33-yard reception on a fake reverse play.

videos.headline: Corrales elevates for 26-yard reception
videos.description: Beau Corrales leaps for a catch that helps set up a UNC field goal.

videos.headline: Rosier hits Herndon for 51-yard TD
videos.description: Christopher Herndon IV catches the pass from Malik Rosier, spins off of a defender and takes it 51-yards for the first touchdown of the game.

videos.headline: Richt calls 1st half 'sloppy'
videos.description: Miami head coach Mark Richt is unimpressed with his teams performance in the first half against UNC.

videos.headline: Miami opens 2nd half with 78-yard TD
videos.description: Miami scores on the first play of the second half when Malik Rosier hits Jeff Thomas for a 78-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Garvin blocks UNC's punt
videos.description: Jonathan Garvin powers through blockers to block the UNC punt.

videos.headline: Trick play leads to UNC TD
videos.description: Wide receiver Anthony Ratliff-Williams takes the lateral pass and throws an 18-yard touchdown to Beau Corrales.

videos.headline: Jackson breaks out the turnover chain
videos.description: Michael Jackson intercepts Nathan Eliott's pass and is awarded Miami's 'turnover chain.'

videos.headline: Perry intercepts Elliott, receives turnover chain
videos.description: Charles Perry takes the turnover chain for himself after intercepting Nathan Elliott.

videos.headline: Berrios extends Miami's lead
videos.description: Braxton Berrios' 5-yard touchdown catch from Malik Rosier puts Miami up 11.

videos.headline: Redwine thinks his INT is Top 10 worthy
videos.description: Sheldrick Redwine holds up sign that says 'SC Top 10" after intercepting Nathan Elliot.

videos.headline: Britt picks off Rosier
videos.description: J.K. Britt intercepts Malik Rosier.

videos.headline: Corrales dives into end zone for his 2nd TD
videos.description: Nathan Elliott passes to Beau Corrales who dives into the end zone for a touchdown.

videos.headline: UNC jumps on Homer fumble
videos.description: Aaron Crawford recovers the Travis Homer fumble.

videos.headline: UNC's drive ends on Brown's fumble
videos.description: Jordon Brown's fourth quarter fumble ends a potential game-winning drive for the Tar Heels.

videos.headline: Richt happy with defensive performance
videos.description: Mark Richt credits his defense in their 24-19 win over UNC

videos.headline: Berrios says'will to win' key in close games
videos.description: Miami's Braxton Berrios knew the offense had to step up and help the defense in the second half against UNC.
